$$

The trace of the identity matrix $I_4$ is 4:

$$
T = 4 (a \cdot b)(c \cdot d) \cdot 	ext{Tr}(I_4) = 4 (a \cdot b)(c \cdot d) \cdot 4 = 16 (a \cdot b)(c \cdot d)
